{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id6b63b26f-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s701n–2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"701n–2"},"text":"§ 701n–2.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Monthly report to Congress","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In fiscal year 2018, and each fiscal year thereafter, the Chief of Engineers of the U.S. Army Corps of Engineers shall transmit to the Congress, after reasonable opportunity for comment, but without change, by the Assistant Secretary of the Army for Civil Works, a monthly report, the first of which shall be transmitted to Congress not later than 2 days after the date of enactment of this subdivision [subdiv. 1 of div. B of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/123"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–123","children":[],"tail":"] and monthly thereafter, which includes detailed estimates of damages to each Corps of Engineers project, caused by natural disasters or otherwise."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id6b63b270-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/123/dB/tIV/s20401"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–123, div. B, title IV, § 20401","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-02-09"},"text":"Feb. 9, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/79"},"text":"132 Stat. 79","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id6b63b271-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id6b63b272-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id6b63b273-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The date of enactment of this subdivision, referred to in text, is the date of enactment of subdiv. 1 of div. B of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/123"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–123","children":[],"tail":", which was approved "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-02-09"},"text":"Feb. 9, 2018","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
